Package frogger

Class Animal

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.image.ImageView
frogger.Actor
frogger.Animal
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class Animal
extends Actor
Creates the character (for this game it's a frog) for the game This class is essential because : It controls the movement according the keys the user pressed Checks and handles what to do if characters interacts with other objects (deaths and points)
